ra County|Hunedoara]]\n| HD\n| [[Deva, Romania|Deva]]\n| 7,063\n|-\n| [[Ialomi\u0163a County|Ialomi\u0163a]]\n| IL\n| [[Slobozia]]\n| 4,453\n|-\n| [[Ia\u015fi County|Ia\u015fi]]\n| IS\n| [[Ia\u015fi]]\n| 5,476\n|-\n| [[Ilfov County|Ilfov]]\n| IF\n| [[Buftea]]\n| 1,583\n|-\n| [[Maramure\u0219 County|Maramure\u0219]]\n| MM\n| [[Baia Mare]]\n| 6,304\n|-\n| [[Mehedin\u0163i County|Mehedin\u0163i]]\n| MH\n| [[Drobeta-Turnu Severin]]\n| 4,933\n|-\n| [[Mure\u015f County|Mure\u015f]]\n| MS\n| [[T\u00e2rgu Mure\u015f]]\n| 6,714\n|-\n| [[Neam\u0163 County|Neam\u0163]]\n| NT\n| [[Piatra Neam\u0163]]\n| 5,896\n|-\n| [[Olt County|Olt]]\n| OT\n| [[Slatina, Romania|Slatina]]\n| 5,498\n|-\n| [[Prahova County|Prahova]]\n| PH\n| [[Ploie\u015fti]]\n| 4,716\n|-\n| [[Satu Mare County|Satu Mare]]\n| SM\n| [[Satu Mare]]\n| 4,418\n|-\n| [[S\u0103laj County|S\u0103laj]]\n| SJ\n| [[Zal\u0103u]]\n| 3,864\n|-\n| [[Sibiu County|Sibiu]]\n| SB\n| [[Sibiu]]\n| 5,432\n|-\n| [[Suceava County|Suceava]]\n| SV\n| [[Suceava]]\n| 8,553\n|-\n| [[Teleorman County|Teleorman]]\n| TR\n| [[Alexandria, Romania|Alexandria]]\n| 5,790\n|-\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| TM\n| [[Timi\u0219oara]]\n| 8,697\n|-\n| [[Tulcea County|Tulcea]]\n| TL\n| [[Tulcea]]\n| 8,499\n|-\n| [[Vaslui County|Vaslui]]\n| VS\n| [[Vaslui]]\n| 5,318\n|-\n| [[V\u00e2lcea County|V\u00e2lcea]]\n| VL\n| [[R\u00e2mnicu V\u00e2lcea]]\n| 5,765\n|-\n| [[Vrancea County|Vrancea]]\n| VN\n| [[Foc\u015fani]]\n| 4,857\n|-\n| [[Bucharest|Bucure\u015fti]]\n| B\n| ''(Bucharest municipality)''\n| 228\n|}</center>\n\n=====Municipalities of Romania=====\n[[Municipalities of Romania]]\n* [[Capital (political)|Capital]] of Romania: [[Capital of Romania|Bucharest]]\n* [[List of cities in Romania|Cities of Romania]]\n\n===Demography of Romania===\n[[Demographics of Romania]]\n\n===Neighbours of Romania===\n* [[Ukraine]]\n* [[Moldavia]]\n* [[Bulgaria]]\n* [[Serbia]]\n* [[Hungary]]\n\n==Government and politics of Romania==\n{{Main|Government of Romania|Politi