omania)|Antena 1]]\n** [[Billa (supermarket)|Billa]]\n** [[Angst (supermarket)|Angst]]\n** [[La Fourmi]]\n** [[Vodafone Romania]]\n** [[Orange Romania]]\n** [[Romanian Television]]\n** [[List of newspapers in Romania]]\n** [[Automobile Dacia]]\n* [[Currency|Currency of Romania]]: [[Romanian leu|Leu]]\n** [[ISO 4217]]: [[Romanian leu|RON]]\n* [[Energy in Romania]]\n** [[Energy policy of Romania]]\n** [[Oil industry in Romania]]\n* [[Mining in Romania]]\n* [[Tourism in Romania]]\n* [[Bucharest Stock Exchange]]\n* [[Sibiu Stock Exchange]]\n* [[Health care in Romania]]\n* [[Transport in Romania]]\n** [[List of airports in Romania|Airports in Romania]]\n** [[Rail transport in Romania]]\n** [[Roads in Romania]]\n* [[Water supply and sanitation in Romania]]\n\n==Education in Romania==\n[[Education in Romania]]\n* [[List of universities in Romania]]\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Romania|European Union}}\n{{InterWiki|Romanian language|code=ro}}\n\n[[Romania]]\n* [[Index of Romania-related articles]]\n* [[List of international rankings]]\n* [[List of Romania-related topics]]\n* [[Member state of the European Union]]\n* [[Member state of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization]]\n* [[Member state of the United Nations]]\n* [[Outline of Europe]]\n* [[Outline of geography]]\n\n(place the links from the following sections into the outline above)\n; Geography\n* [[Protected areas in Romania|Protected areas]]\n* [[Topography of Romania|Topography]]\n\n; Politics\n* [[Administrative divisions of Romania|Administrative divisions]]\n* [[Constitution of Romania|Constitution]]\n* [[Elections in Romania|Elections]]\n* [[Foreign relations of Romania|Foreign relations]]\n* [[Government of Romania|Government]]\n* [[Human rights in Romania|Human rights]]\n** [[LGBT rights in Romania|LGBT]]\n* [[LGBT history in Romania|LGBT history]]\n* [[Courts in Romania|Judiciary]]\n* [[Law enforcement in Romania|Law enforcement]]\n* [[Military of Romania|Military]]\n* [[Parliament of Romania|Parliament]]\n* [[